description:
Puzzletronics: Digital Infinite is a minimalist jigsaw-puzzle. The player must move the pieces to form logical circuits while listen to a relaxing and calm soundtrack.

Challenge yourself through 135 different levels with a variety of difficulty in them, learning the behavior of logical doors and digital logic. The game presents an intuitive gameplay that dispenses tutorials.

Features:
- More than a 130 different levels with random pieces disposal;
- A minimalist environment;
- Calm and relaxing soundtrack;
- A big variety of pieces.

Developed by IdunaSoft and published by QUByte Interactive
